arena-hard-auto
===============

The prompts in evaluator/datasets/arena_hard_v2_subset.yaml are imported
verbatim from the arena-hard-auto benchmark and are used under the Apache
License, Version 2.0.

  Source : https://github.com/lmarena/arena-hard-auto
  File   : data/arena-hard-v2.0/question.jsonl
  Ref    : 196f6b826783b3da7310e361a805fa36f0be83f3 (main)
  License: Apache-2.0 — https://github.com/lmarena/arena-hard-auto/blob/main/LICENSE

Each imported case preserves its upstream `uid` as the LLMeter case `id` for
traceability. Only a balanced subset of prompts is included; no upstream source
code is vendored. Regenerate via:

  python scripts/import_arena_hard.py --source <path-to-question.jsonl>

